{"tid":23712,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果：iPhone 6s電池異常問題的元兇為空氣","createTime":"2016-12-05T06:08:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T12:04:52.000Z","uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a3488b57f74731b26cd927fad4695ededf362ddb","tid":23712,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T06:08:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/110016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ithome.com.tw%2Fnews%2F110016&d=aWm579aYkHvvwdD7ZyOwrHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=62f17902\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ithome.com.tw/news/110016</a><br />\n<br />\n11月中國傳出多起iPhone 6及6s在電池電量未耗盡的情形下自動關機，蘋果調查後指出可能是2015年9至10月生產的手機中，某電子元件包進電池組前在空氣中曝露過久所倄，導致電池耗電異常、自動關機，將為發生問題的用戶更換電池。<br />\n<br />\niPhone 6s、6s Plus傳出電池異常關機事件，蘋果調查後，將原因歸咎於電路元件不當暴露於空氣中的關係。<br />\n<br />\n11月中國傳出多起iPhone 6及6s在電池電量未耗盡的情形下自動關機，引起上海市消費者權益保護委員會關注，約談蘋果公司代表，蘋果承諾將對事件原因進行調查，同時為發生問題的消費者更換電池。<br />\n <br />\n根據蘋果支援網頁指出，在2015年9到10月間生產的iPhone 6s中的某個電子元件包進電池組之前，在受控的空氣中暴露過長時間，使電池耗電超出正常水準，並導致意外關機。蘋果表示目前沒有發現其他原因。<br />\n <br />\n蘋果強調這並非安全問題，而是iPhone在設計時刻意允許在一定條件下關機，像是極低溫環境中，以避免電子元件因電壓過低造成損傷而關機。<br />\n <br />\n蘋果將針對這批手機提供免費更換電池的服務，也公佈網頁，提供用戶以序號查詢是否符合免費更換的條件，以及可提供服務的授權經銷商及蘋果專賣店。"},{"pid":"7af3fd43012f4e61faad87f467a19b7e66d06763","tid":23712,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T07:25:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d3489e0ad7fbddc1c994278df02f9ef5b179ed0","tid":23712,"uid":31452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"即係啲電嘅packing有問題喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83ff41d4dd74d18b7bd9e2b96f344c78cac816db","tid":23712,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T08:33:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係啲電嘅packing有問題喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正是，係Apple問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a06c4ffaba7382eeab2b719027ecaf7723bd924","tid":23712,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T10:47:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"417e26c0e56e265b02083701ec1f64357869e4e8","tid":23712,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:50:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好過某公司啲「外來熱力」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n某公司就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dceb4fa87b1c2d161a8a77298fc0d1eeda677359","tid":23712,"uid":47618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:56:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好過某公司啲「外來熱力」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n某公司就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n某乜撚呀，三星就三星啦講事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"307ed7ad63bb60016ad3e9b591050082596ecc84","tid":23712,"uid":17799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:57:05.000Z","msg":"有冇網頁link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我6仔90%就自己熄機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"753b0af1e6d2b07fc6cf6f1dea08eb56fcd25fef","tid":23712,"uid":1557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T11:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好過某公司啲「外來熱力」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只要有人差過apple，apple有咩問題都唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df3c6eb10c5896e9aa292f718217c2cd331dd0a9","tid":23712,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-05T12:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好過某公司啲「外來熱力」</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n只要有人差過apple，apple有咩問題都唔係問題<img src=\"/assets/f